      <title>穆迪表示南非政府的下一步改革任务艰巨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/next-south-african-government-has-tough-reform-job-moody-s-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪投资者服务公司警告称，如果本月选举后出现联合政府，南非可能难以在解决该国长期面临的挑战方面取得更大进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/next-south-african-government-has-tough-reform-job-moody-s-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 14:06:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚酋长因报警而受到攻击，其工作仍不稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/columbia-chief-assailed-for-calling-cops-keeps-shaky-hold-on-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚大学校长米努什·沙菲克决定允许警察在校园停留两周，这可能会帮助她避免常春藤盟校领导人的命运，这些领导人因处理抗议和反犹太主义指控的方式而被迫辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/columbia-chief-assailed-for-calling-cops-keeps-shaky-hold-on-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 13:52:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯称正在以“积极精神”研究停战协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/hamas-says-cease-fire-deal-being-studied-in-positive-spirit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯正在本着“积极的精神”研究一项与以色列临时停火的提议，因为国际社会对双方施加的压力越来越大，要求双方达成协议并结束这场震动中东的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/hamas-says-cease-fire-deal-being-studied-in-positive-spirit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 13:41:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>领导层动荡后苏格兰民族主义者向老手求助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/scottish-nationalists-look-to-old-hand-after-leadership-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[约翰·斯温尼 (John Swinney) 表示，他曾多次试图退出前线政治，去年他宣布退出。现在，他似乎回来了，并面临着职业生涯中最大的挑战之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/scottish-nationalists-look-to-old-hand-after-leadership-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 13:41:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>假化肥可能导致肯尼亚农业部长下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/fake-fertilizer-may-lead-to-kenyan-agriculture-minister-s-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚立法者要求解职该国农业部长，原因是政府机构通过补贴计划分发假化肥，这是总统威廉·鲁托政府遭遇的最新丑闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/fake-fertilizer-may-lead-to-kenyan-agriculture-minister-s-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 13:33:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯·格里芬资助反对麦卡锡罢免背后的立法者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ken-griffin-funds-push-against-lawmaker-behind-mccarthy-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[城堡投资公司的肯·格里芬 (Ken Griffin) 正在资助一项活动，以击败前众议院议长凯文·麦卡锡 (Kevin McCarthy) 下台背后的保守派之一，从而重塑严重分裂的共和党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ken-griffin-funds-push-against-lawmaker-behind-mccarthy-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>团体称奥夫拉多尔选举法官的提议破坏了民主</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/amlo-s-proposal-to-elect-judges-undermines-democracy-groups-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三个法律和倡导团体周四表示，墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔提出的宪法改革对司法独立构成威胁，违反国际法律标准并破坏民主。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/amlo-s-proposal-to-elect-judges-undermines-democracy-groups-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
